            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and honestly, I'm still processing how fast it works. You type a description of what you want—like \"a project management app with Kanban boards and team chat\"—and the AI generates a complete, functional application in seconds. No drag-and-drop. No wireframes. No waiting for a developer to free up.",
