        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Base44 ships updates frequently, and a few recent additions stand out:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plan Mode",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is a game-changer for complex apps. When you enable Plan Mode, the AI doesn't just build—it first creates a detailed blueprint of your application. You see the structure, the data models, the page hierarchy. You approve or adjust the plan before any code gets generated. For anything beyond a simple tool, this prevents the \"that's not what I meant\" problem.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Super Agents",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The newest feature on the platform. Super Agents are specialized AI assistants that handle specific domains—think of them as expert consultants built into your workflow. They bring deeper knowledge to particular types of applications, which means sharper outputs for niche projects.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Platform Migration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Already have something built elsewhere? Base44 now supports migrating from other platforms. This alone saves hours of rebuilding and makes the switch feel risk-free.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Speech Recognition",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can now dictate your app descriptions via voice input. It sounds minor, but when you're brainstorming features out loud, speaking is faster than typing. Especially useful on mobile.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
