      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Base44 Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not every tool is for everyone, and I appreciate that. Here's who gets the most value from Base44:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Solo founders and indie hackers.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You have an idea. You need an MVP yesterday. Base44 lets you go from concept to working product in an afternoon. That speed advantage is massive when you're validating ideas.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Freelancers and agencies.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Building apps for clients becomes a service you can offer at a fraction of traditional costs. Higher margins, faster delivery, happier clients.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Non-technical team leads.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You manage a team, you see bottlenecks that a simple internal tool would fix, but you've always depended on engineering resources. Now you build the solution yourself.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Students and educators.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Learning about software architecture by watching AI build apps from descriptions is incredibly instructive. It's a teaching tool disguised as a builder.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small business owners.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Need a booking system? An inventory tracker? A customer feedback portal? These are exactly the kinds of applications Base44 excels at—and you won't need to hire anyone.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-base44-by-wix"
