      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Base44 Feels Different from Other No-Code Tools",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've used plenty of no-code platforms. The usual workflow involves dragging components, connecting databases, configuring triggers, and testing—repeatedly. It's powerful, but it's still manual work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Base44 removes that manual layer almost entirely. You're not assembling an app piece by piece. You're describing an outcome, and the AI assembles it for you. The mental model shifts from \"building\" to \"directing.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That doesn't mean you lose control. You can refine everything through conversation. But the starting point is a complete application, not a blank canvas. That psychological difference matters more than you'd expect.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
