        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Base44 offers a free tier that lets you build and test applications without paying. You can explore the platform, generate apps, and iterate on your ideas. Paid plans unlock additional features, higher usage limits, and priority support for production-ready applications.",
