      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Base44 generates fully functional applications—not mockups or prototypes. Users have built client portals, internal dashboards, booking systems, and networking apps that run in production. The key is being specific in your descriptions and iterating until the app meets your standards.",
