      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Base44 compresses development time from weeks or months to minutes or hours. A simple internal tool that might cost $5,000-$15,000 with a developer can be built on Base44 with a subscription. It's not a replacement for complex enterprise software with custom architecture, but for most business applications, it delivers tremendous value at a fraction of the cost.",
